   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00227"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Gustav Schwarzkopf</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51">Wien I</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207296">Tiefer
                        Graben 23</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00228"/><salute>Lieber Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav,</salute>das ist mein vorläufiges Programm</p><p><hi rend="underline" n="1"><date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date></hi>
                (<date>17</date>) <rs type="place" ref="#pmb860">Graz</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb35493">Steinach</rs> (Bahn) – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb35496">Schladming</rs> (Rad)</p><p><date>Montag 18.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb35496">Schladming</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb41003">Bi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chofshofen</rs> (Rad–) – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40336">Zell a S.</rs>
                  (Bahn<supplied>)</supplied></p><p><date><hi rend="underline" n="1">Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tg</hi> 19.</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40336">Zell am See</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34191">Bruck</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb305739">Fu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch</rs>.</p><p><date><hi rend="underline" n="1">Mittwoch</hi> 20</date> (<rs type="place" ref="#pmb40632">Ferleiten</rs>), <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34191">Bruck</rs> – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb521">Bad-Ga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</rs></p><p>Bis <date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date> etwa <rs type="place" ref="#pmb521">Ga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</rs>; da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> per Rad <rs type="place" ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</rs>; wo ich jedenfalls von <date>Montag
                  (25)</date> – <date>Do<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tg 28.</date> bin. –
               Eventuelle <hi rend="underline" n="1">telegr.</hi> Adre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e <rs type="place" ref="#pmb35493">Steinach</rs>; Briefe <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34014">Wildbad
                  Ga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein, Villa Wa<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ing</rs>.</p><closer>Auf Wieder<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehn<lb/> Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
